// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0506 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 597524b7-4f30-523f-9b95-04d50e3a871c

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:9*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
